;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/cmGOFw6HawM&quot; >;百思买&lt;/a>;——无需会员资格。 256GB 版本也在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BJLBNNRT?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a 上发售>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/cmGOJnYsvDy&quot;>;Best Buy&lt;/a>; 的价格创历史新低，为 449 美元（折扣 50 美元），不过某些颜色确实需要在亚马逊上订阅 Prime。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;6KOuGV&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;: [{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;在 iPadOS 18 中，整个 iPad 就是一个计算器应用&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24194423/math-notes-ipad-ios -18-calculator-app&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;如何安装 iOS 18 公共测试版&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24198819/ios-18-public-betas- install-how-to&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;这是 Prime Day 最后一天我们最喜欢的技术优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24200040/amazon-prime- day-best-tech-deals-gadgets-2024&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;J1S8B8&quot;>;Apple 的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/23418039/apple-ipad-review-10th-gen-2022-10-9-tablet-ipados&quot;>;最新的入门级 iPad&lt;/a>; 感觉比即将推出的第九代机型更加现代，并且目前的折扣，购买街区里的新孩子可能更有意义。苹果将​​屏幕拉伸至 10.9 英寸，并更新了设计，使其看起来更相似。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/ 24200665/amazon-prime-day-apple-ipad-10th-gen-deal-sale-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200665/amazon-prime-day-apple-ipad-10th-gen-deal-sale-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200665/amazon-prime-day-apple-ipad-10th-gen-deal-sale-2024</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-17T18:50:37-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-17T18:50:37-04:00</updated><title> NASA 取消了原本在月球上寻找水源的 VIPER 漫游车</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;NASA VIPER 的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/nFaYCf45RDYtqCM10uZucyXQa9I=/300x0:3540x2160/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73467044/nasa_viper.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：&lt;a class=&quot;ql-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.nasa.gov/news-release/nasa-to-announce-selection-of-company-to-fly-viper-rover -to-moon/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;NASA/Daniel Rutter&lt;/a>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;eespCR&quot;>;NASA 没有推进其 VIPER 计划（Volatiles 的缩写）调查极地探索漫游车——旨在将漫游车放在月球背面寻找水源。周三，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nasa.gov/news-release/nasa-ends-viper-project-continues-moon-exploration/&quot;>;美国宇航局称成本增加&lt;/a>;和一些延误取消该项目的原因。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Xg5huW&quot;>;VIPER 最初预计&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21287806/nasa-astrobotic-viper-water-moon -rover&quot;>;2023 年底发射&lt;/a>;。然而，由于供应链和日程安排延误，NASA 将日期推迟到 2025 年 9 月。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Tc0H08&quot;>;Astrobotic，是&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/11/24035242/astrobotic-peregrine-lunar-lander-nasa 背后的同一家公司-data-payloads&quot;>;命运多舛的游隼月球着陆器&lt;/a>;，本应在其格里芬航天器上发射 VIPER。尽管 VIPER 被取消，Astrobotic 将&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/23/24047818/nasa-moon-landing-private-missions-failure-astrobotic-spacex&quot;>;继续与美国宇航局&lt;/a>;“不早于”2025 年秋季在没有月球车的情况下让格里芬着陆器登陆月球。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;0w1KLq&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot; data-dnt=&quot; true&quot;align=&quot;center&quot;>; &lt;p lang=&quot;en&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>;A...&lt;/p>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200807/nasa-viper-rover-project-canceled-water-moon&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200807/nasa-viper-rover-project-canceled-water-moon" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200807/nasa-viper-rover-project-canceled-water-moon</id><author